Tyrael sent a massive bolt of light straight at Perceptor. The battle 
was tight and he knew they'd have to pull out before long. Shadow Star 
seemed battle-worn and it was obvious he needed some repairs.

Tyrael: Come and get this, Predafreaks!

Burrock lanced out with his tentacles, trying to reach for Waspinator 
or Quickstrike.
